'''''Hate''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|Nebulon-B frigate]] that attempted to stop ''[[Yali]]'' and [[Maria (MC80 Star Cruiser)|''Maria'']] on their way to [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]. It was destroyed on that attempt by combined efforts of [[Fleet/Legends|fleets]] and [[Red Squadron (Rebel Alliance)/Legends|Red Squadron's]] [[A/SF-01 B-wing starfighter/Legends|B-wings]].

